{"tid":922504,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"（你問我答）好多樹葉 砌一幅畫","createTime":"2018-11-30T12:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T16:06:19.000Z","uid":143257,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e94cf20be8b6194fd58ce6c7a04c289e676e18","tid":922504,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"隔左一年再開post 依舊仲做緊藝術<br />\n今次分享都係樹葉砌畫<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qtcfbd3v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqtcfbd3v&h=601b93ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ntimelapse過程 其實我覺得呢個過程都幾特別<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BbO4zo5AuAo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBbO4zo5AuAo%2F&d=Rw8TgxYCWyBNPWI9w6ck110Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3fd88a7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBbO4zo5AuAo%2F&h=05839709\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BbO4zo5AuAo/</a><br />\n<br />\n其次係其實砌完第一次樹葉作品後 <br />\n發覺其實樹葉係會因日照曬而由綠變黃 黃變白<br />\n<br />\n作品完成第一日<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dky7gu32\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdky7gu32&h=47b92b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五日後<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n1i5tvg6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn1i5tvg6&h=77962aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十日後<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/esk3n79z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fesk3n79z&h=772ad752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知一定好多人會問保存問題<br />\n樹葉會變色<br />\n而會否腐爛方面 第一幅作品至今近近兩年 仍然保存良好 無任何腐爛跡象 <br />\n不過如果有巴打有唔同建議 隨便提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外 如果有巴打係任何方面諗到cross over 或合作/野玩<br />\n可以ig inbox我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後如果大家中意同想睇多d 不如follow 我art.ig 同facebook page<br />\n支持下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nig : gllh_art (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgllh_art%2F&d=Rw8TgxYCWyBNPWI9w6ck110Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=dd9d9c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/</a>)<br />\nfb page : Giraffe leung lok hei (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gllhart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgllhart%2F&d=Rw8TgxYCWyBNPWI9w6ck110Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0e3972fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gllhart/</a>)"},{"pid":"a2c2476ff28d8a341ea5fd5ef5e00c62dcef5ba0","tid":922504,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"易唔易燃?"},{"pid":"f6cfd61d1ffdf54bfc48f5533364039a27b5196c","tid":922504,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c2476ff28d8a341ea5fd5ef5e00c62dcef5ba0","tid":922504,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"易唔易燃?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"冇用火燒過 亦冇曾經起過火<br />\n巴打有用火玩 既諗頭？"},{"pid":"27ddc216e71d3d4c35f293a67cc16f2e156ac40c","tid":922504,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"但我諗得番啲葉脈纖維 應該唔易燃"},{"pid":"e78b98568797bb43f165f23c0addc31b906c21bc","tid":922504,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6cfd61d1ffdf54bfc48f5533364039a27b5196c","tid":922504,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c2476ff28d8a341ea5fd5ef5e00c62dcef5ba0","tid":922504,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"易唔易燃?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"冇用火燒過 亦冇曾經起過火<br />\n巴打有用火玩 既諗頭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:20:42.000Z","msg":"見你講保存<br />\n諗到全部都係葉<br />\n風高物燥會唔會好易著火"},{"pid":"d81d058387e8d064aec6