s/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"見你用過毫子做<br />\n可唔可以share 下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T00:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCWjzy4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCWjzy4.png&h=cdb8a434&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U16WBNq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU16WBNq.png&h=1710e8d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅作品係用兩毫子砌魚蝦蟹<br />\n不過想係呢個post主要講樹葉<br />\n多謝巴打咁都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85542a54717692971a88aa7884e3797e4e8c5ba","tid":922504,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"好得閒？"},{"pid":"9a53d504cd5356e5feb1ca0a9455ae0f83c8ebcd","tid":922504,"uid":224673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:52:10.000Z","msg":"好撚勁"},{"pid":"a78f25e4b7c4b0113256fb45e5644186d278d5f4","tid":922504,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"點解當初有咁既念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7efc0e60bb2dcefd808b434a0a8b788d770a71","tid":922504,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a78f25e4b7c4b0113256fb45e5644186d278d5f4","tid":922504,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"點解當初有咁既念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"好直接 想做藝術<br />\n但又唔想淨係紙筆 <br />\n同當然自覺紙筆畫畫技巧唔夠獨特<br />\n所以 想試下唔想物料畫畫<br />\n其實樹葉之前 亦試左唔少其他野 <br />\n之後 亦keep住有試"},{"pid":"ee3f9802ef1464d4cc52c4b7cde1768174c55e8f","tid":922504,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.